  "body": "<!--\r\n\r\n    Please do *NOT* ask usage questions in Github issues.\r\n\r\n    If your issue is not a feature request or bug report use:\r\n    https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/prometheus-users. If\r\n    you are unsure whether you hit a bug, search and ask in the\r\n    mailing list first.\r\n\r\n    You can find more information at: https://prometheus.io/community/\r\n\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**What did you do?**\r\n\r\nReview code, I saw different file permission in the repository, mostly is `0644` or `0666`\r\n\r\n**What did you expect to see?**\r\n\r\nFile permission should mostly be consistent for some reason . `0644` is a common choice, for example safety .\r\n\r\nThe circumstance of using `0666` looks like rarely.\r\n\r\n**What did you see instead? Under which circumstances?**\r\n\r\nThere are at least two values for file permission.\r\n\r\n1. `0644`\r\n```\r\ncmd/promtool/archive.go\r\n24:const filePerm = 0644\r\n\r\ntsdb/fileutil/flock_solaris.go\r\n48:\tf, err := os.OpenFile(fileName, os.O_RDWR|os.O_CREATE, 0644)\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n2. `0666`\r\n\r\n```\r\ntsdb/wal.go\r\n507:\tf, err := os.OpenFile(name, os.O_RDWR, 0666)\r\n\r\npromql/query_logger.go\r\n85:\tfile, err := os.OpenFile(filename, os.O_CREATE|os.O_RDWR|os.O_TRUNC, 0666)\r\n```\r\n\r\n* Prometheus version:\r\n\r\n\tmaster branch\r\n\r\nNote:\r\n\r\nThe `kind/bug` label may be no accurate for the issue, but different file permission may lead to some maintain problem .",
